				<div  class="WINDOW-BODY" >
Magelo was founded by Christian Meunier, a dedicated gamer, in his college dorm room in 2001. Christian (a.k.a Jelan) initially created a system to make Everquest character profiles solely for his guildmates. However, the character profiles spread quickly and soon Magelo was born, serving hundreds of thousands of users.
<br><br>
With our deeply personal roots as gaming purists, Magelo does not modify game play in any way, nor do we offer any information that is not already available to players through the games themselves. Magelo seeks only to enrich players gaming experience, both in and out of the game, by providing database, character profiling, signature, and social networking tools. 
<br><br>
Our proprietary software client, <a href="magelo_sync.jspa">Magelo Sync</a>, is a reliable game data collector, as well as a synchronization and authentication tool for Magelo character profiles. No more inaccurate databases, out-of-date rosters, or painful profile updates!
<br><br>
To have a better understanding of players needs, we maintain a close relationship with the online gaming community via our forums, gaming conventions, and other channels. Feel free to <a href="contact_us.jspa">contact us</a> if you have any suggestions or comments! We are always open to new business opportunities as well.
<br><br>
This site would not be possible without all the volunteer advisors who keep the wheels turning. A HUGE thanks to you guys!
<br><br>

<div class="WINDOW-BODY-TITLE"><img src="http://cdn.magelo.com/images/website/localized/picto/eq_puce_orange.png?v=21" height="12" alt="" width="12" class="png32" />&nbsp;No Ads! policy</div>
<br>
As you have probably noticed, there are no ads on our website. That's the result of our No Ads! policy. We feel strongly that a gaming community website like ours should focus on just one thing: entertainment! <br><br>
Of course, our No Ads! policy has a cost. We strive to create a safe haven for those who want to rest their minds and take a break from everyday life. All of this wouldn't be possible if it weren't for our Premium subscribers (thank you!). If you like our services would like to take them to the next level, please consider upgrading to a <a href="premium.jspa">Premium Subscription</a>! 

</div>
